{"chapters": {"overview": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A TRILHA DO INICIANTE</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">NOOB</span> <span class=\"bd\">TO PRO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Wikibooks (comunidade)</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Fundamentos antes do clique</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> livro insiste: <strong>entenda coordenadas XYZ, espaço local × global e projeção ortográfica × perspectiva ANTES de modelar.</strong> Sem o vocabulário…</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Metáfora do livro</div><div class=\"tipbody\">não dá pra pilotar sem entender os instrumentos.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Aprenda na ORDEM certa</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">C</span>ada lição pressupõe a anterior: você não aprende UV antes de saber o que é uma face. <strong>É essa sequência por dependência que o manual (referência pura)…</strong></p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">referência responde 'o quê'; trilha responde 'quando' e 'por quê'.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Projetos concretos</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">C</span>asa, chapéu, taça, personagem com ossos. <strong>Cada conceito é ancorado num objeto real</strong> — não numa explicação abstrata de parâmetro.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Prática</div><div class=\"tipbody\">termine cada mini-projeto antes de avançar.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">4</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Ressalva honesta de versão</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">P</span>or ser wiki comunitária, <strong>muitos tutoriais foram escritos p/ Blender 2.4–2.7</strong> (antes do redesign do 2.8+). Os conceitos valem; <strong>os…</strong></p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">confie no conceito, valide o atalho no Blender que você usa.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch01-fundamentos-navegacao": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">CAPÍTULO 1 DE 3</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">NOOB</span> <span class=\"bd\">TO PRO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Wikibooks (comunidade)</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Fundamentos e Navegação</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Coordenadas e Espaços</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">X</span>, Y, Z; espaço global × local; ortográfico × perspectiva.</strong> Um objeto rotacionado tem eixos locais diferentes dos globais — entender isso evita que mover/girar pareça aleatório.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Base</div><div class=\"tipbody\">sem este vocabulário, nenhum transform faz sentido.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Fundamentos e Navegação</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Navegar a viewport</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">G</span>irar (botão do meio), pan (Shift+meio), zoom (scroll), Numpad p/ vistas fixas. <strong>Fluência aqui vale mais que qualquer ferramenta</strong> — sem ela, todo trabalho trava.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Prática</div><div class=\"tipbody\">decore Numpad 1/3/7 (frente/lado/topo) e 5 (orto↔persp).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Fundamentos e Navegação</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\"><em>TAB</em>: Object × Edit</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span>bject Mode move o objeto inteiro; Edit Mode expõe vértices/arestas/faces. <strong>A troca (TAB) define o fluxo inteiro de modelagem.</strong> Os 3 modos de seleção (1/2/3) resolvem problemas diferentes.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">'estou editando o objeto ou a geometria dele?'</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide lessons\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOBTO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Fundamentos e Navegação</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Lições-Chave do Capítulo 1</h1><ul class=\"lessons-list\"><li><span class=\"lnum\">1</span>Domine coordenadas e espaços antes de modelar.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">2</span>Navegação fluida da viewport é pré-requisito de tudo.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">3</span>TAB (Object↔Edit) é a distinção mais fundamental do Blender.</li></ul></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Este é só 1 capítulo — o livro <strong>inteiro</strong> em 1 resumo: cheat sheet + PDF no acervo &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch02-modelagem-materiais": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">CAPÍTULO 2 DE 3</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">NOOB</span> <span class=\"bd\">TO PRO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Wikibooks (comunidade)</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Materiais</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Extrude é o verbo</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">E</span></strong> cria geometria nova a partir da existente — é o movimento mais usado da modelagem (a casa, o telhado, tudo nasce dele). Combine com mesclar vértices p/ fechar formas.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Ciclo</div><div class=\"tipbody\">selecionar → Edit → selecionar componente → agir (E, etc.).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Materiais</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\"><em>Normais</em> + Smooth Shading</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">S</span>mooth Shading não adiciona geometria — interpola as normais</strong> p/ um cubo de poucos polígonos parecer liso. Normais invertidas causam sombra errada: <strong>Ctrl+N</strong> recalcula.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Ilusão-chave</div><div class=\"tipbody\">low-poly + smooth shading = curva sem peso de geometria.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOB TO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Materiais</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\"><em>Material × Textura</em></h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">M</span>aterial</strong> = propriedades da superfície (cor, brilho, reflexo). <strong>Textura</strong> = o detalhe que modifica o material (procedural ou imagem).</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">textura sem material não existe; ela é um modificador do material.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide lessons\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">NOOBTO PRO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Materiais</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Lições-Chave do Capítulo 2</h1><ul class=\"lessons-list\"><li><span class=\"lnum\">1</span>Extrude (E) é o movimento central da modelagem.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">2</span>Smooth shading interpola normais — suaviza sem adicionar geometria.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">3</span>Material define a superfície; textura é o detalhe que a modifica.</li></ul></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Este é só 1 capítulo — o livro <strong>inteiro</strong> em 1 resumo: cheat sheet + PDF no acervo &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http: